                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/textviewab2"
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_marginTop="25dp"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/allan"
                    android:text="Interesting Facts and Trivia About Zonal Anthrapological Museum"
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:textSize="22sp"
                    android:textStyle="bold" />
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/textview1gg"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                    android:layout_marginLeft="10dp"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/courgette"
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:textSize="16sp" />
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/textviewac2"
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_marginTop="25dp"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/allan"
                    android:text="How To Reach"
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:textSize="22sp"
                    android:textStyle="bold" />
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/textview1cg"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                    android:layout_marginLeft="10dp"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/courgette"
                    android:text="      The Andamans can be reached both by flight and cruise. There are flights scheduled from major cities like Kolkata, Bangalore and Delhi through Port Blair airport, and also cruises from Vizag, Chennai. Once you arrive at the Andamans, you can go to the mainland, then take available conveyance like buses or taxi to reach the museum."
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:textSize="16sp" />
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/textviewad2"
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_marginTop="25dp"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/allan"
                    android:text="Best Time To Visit"
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:textSize="22sp"
                    android:textStyle="bold" />
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/textview1dg"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                    android:layout_marginLeft="10dp"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/courgette"
                    android:text="      The Andamans have tropical climate, meaning adequately hot summers. At winters, though, it is not chillingly cold, and the weather is ideal for tourists. The monsoons, however are not appropriate times for visiting, as the showers are powerful and potentially dangerous, and you cannot go underwater. The best time to visit starts from November and ends in May"
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:textSize="16sp" />
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/textviewae2"
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_marginTop="25dp"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/allan"
                    android:text="Availability Of Guides"
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:textSize="22sp"
                    android:textStyle="bold" />
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/textview1eg"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                    android:layout_marginLeft="10dp"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/courgette"
                    android:text="      Guides are very important components of a tour, and they are available for hire locally at varied prices, some regulated. There are also guides you can take with you as part of the tour, or those locals you can engage to show you around. The guide has to be knowledgeable, and understandable to you. Moreover, the museum has plenty of directions and information on the displayed species even if you are alone as well."
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:textSize="16sp" />
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/textviewaF2"
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_marginTop="25dp"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/allan"
                    android:text="Transport Facilities"
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:textSize="22sp"
                    android:textStyle="bold" />
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/textviewafa"
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_marginTop="20dp"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/courgette"
                    android:text="* Local Bus"
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:textSize="16sp"
                    android:textStyle="bold"/>
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/textview1fg"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                    android:layout_marginLeft="10dp"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/courgette"
                    android:text="      Mohanpura bus terminus is the central terminus. The buses working hours are from 4:30 am to 12 noon. The buses transport within port Blair is available all through the day. Private travel services also provide buses for travelling within Port Blair and other parts of Andaman, from Mohanpura terminus."
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:textSize="16sp" />
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/textviewaga"
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_marginTop="20dp"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/courgette"
                    android:text="* Cabs"
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:textSize="16sp"
                    android:textStyle="bold"/>
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/textview12g"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                    android:layout_marginLeft="10dp"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/courgette"
                    android:text="      Private travel companies in Andaman provide cab services from airport(Arrival Hall)and Mohanpura central terminus. These are pre-paid taxi services, available for dropping the tourists to various destinations from the airport. So check in advance about the cost the taxis charge. Other than this, auto rickshaw and mini buses are also available for local transport."
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:textSize="16sp" />
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/textviewaha"
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_marginTop="20dp"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/courgette"
                    android:text="* Rental"
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:textSize="16sp"
                    android:textStyle="bold"/>
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/textview1hg"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                    android:layout_marginLeft="10dp"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/courgette"
                    android:text="      Rental services for two wheeler vehicles is another option. Hiring a two wheeler and going around the nearby places connected to the island, is a good option. People can also hire bicycles and explore small islands like Havelock and Neil Island. Andaman World Travels, Welcome to Andaman and Andaman Travelers are some of the travel companies providing cars, two wheeler and bicycles for rent."
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:textSize="16sp" />
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/textviewaia"
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_marginTop="20dp"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/courgette"
